STATE of North Carolina
v.
John Thomas JONES, III. No. 532P07. Supreme Court of North Carolina. December 6, 2007. John T. Jones, III, Pro Se. Amy C. Kunstling, Assistant Attorney General, James C. Gaither, Jr., District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 30th day of October 2007 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Catawba County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 6th day of December 2007."
